  m_Name: SoldierJournal_04
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 49
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xEDnh #4 \u2014 Kho v\u0169 kh\xED"
  category: 1
  content: "Tu\u1EA7n tra khu v\u1EF1c ph\xEDa \u0111\xF4ng, t\xF4i ph\xE1t hi\u1EC7n
    m\u1ED9t nh\xE0 kho b\u1ECF hoang. B\xEAn trong c\xF2n nguy\xEAn th\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA1n
    v\xE0 v\xE0i kh\u1EA9u s\xFAng \u2014 qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i qu\xEAn kh\xF4ng
    thu h\u1ED3i khi r\xFAt. T\xF4i \u0111\xE3 ki\u1EC3m k\xEA: 2 kh\u1EA9u rifle,
    1 kh\u1EA9u shotgun, kho\u1EA3ng 200 vi\xEAn \u0111\u1EA1n. T\xF4i \u0111\u1EC3
    nguy\xEAn t\u1EA1i ch\u1ED7, kh\xF4ng mang theo v\xEC balan \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EA7y.
    N\u1EBFu ai c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng c\u1EA7n v\u0169 kh\xED, \u0111\u1EBFn nh\xE0 kho
    ph\xEDa \u0111\xF4ng khu l\u1EC1u. C\u1EEDa v\u1EABn m\u1EDF. T\xF4i \u0111\xE1nh
    d\u1EA5u b\u1EB1ng v\u1EA1ch \u0111\u1ECF tr\xEAn t\u01B0\u1EDDng. Nh\u1EDB c\u1EA9n
    th\u1EADn \u2014 b\xEAn trong c\xF3 v\xE0i con zombie, t\xF4i \u0111\xE3 x\u1EED
    l\xFD h\u1EBFt nh\u01B0ng c\xF3 th\u1EC3 c\xF3 th\xEAm b\xF2 v\xE0o. B\xE1o c\xE1o:
    H\u1EA1 s\u0129 Miller."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
